channel.title: Wierd character files
channel.description:
Hey Moparscape, I have a problem when I open my character file, all I see are some Hiragana/Kanji symbols... can someone please help me with this ASAP? I am currently trying to make myself owner on my server and therefore are in need of some help. Thank You In Advance,
~Zofis

Thank You r r r, problem fixed before I used notepad and apparently it works better with wordpad… But now I have a bigger problem, I change my rights to 3 and then I compile. When I log in I’m still a regular user. (And No it is not someone else’ s server because I only have my character file in there) any suggestions?[/quote]
What server source is it? When you compile what does it say in the CMD? Some servers you cant see your crown only other people.
